 2010-07642010-06-17,  ,  ,  ,  EC
ActMigratory Birds Convention Act, 1994
SubjectRegulations Amending the Migratory Birds Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the MIGRATORY BIRDS REGULATIONS, in order to change some hunting season dates for the 2010-2011 hunting season and to set daily bag limits and possession limits for migratory game birds to ensure the sustainable harvest of migratory game bird populations. The amendment also creates an earlier opening date for the measures aiming to reduce the size of overabundant Snow Goose populations.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2010-0139 Publication Date: 2010-07-07
